{
  "stem": "9478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So she decided she'll walk back home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I see my mother disappeared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I left the truck in the field after when I let down the chairman from the party.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I left the truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was 29 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it took me a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the tires gave up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I came back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I begged my mother she should come with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she says no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever will happen with everybody will happen with me too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I grabbed the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I came out and standing in front of the house, a power, a [NON-ENGLISH], you know, pushed me in the back and says go away, go away, go away.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not a big believer, especially after this Holocaust what's happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But some other power pushed me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I grabbed the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ran any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to that Novograd Volynsk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I dropped the bicycle, and I jumped on a freight train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for 10 days and 10 nights, I went to Kiev, and to Rostov, to Stalingrad-- farther, farther, farther away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1940--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939, to our town came refugees-- dentists, doctors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us what goes on--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us what goes on, that the Germans are killing Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For what reason?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am not afraid of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm a worker.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not a politician.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know anything about politic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't care who's the government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I never could believe then that gangster will take innocent people-- shoemakers, and carpenters-- and kill them, for what?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mind couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our house was a family from Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
